Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仙女棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}礼花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有好多好多种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么买了这么多 到底想干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱喜欢哪种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烟花棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 是你买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 是红叶拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我计划明天晚上大家一起去放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么是明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想啊 我们不是准备后天就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一惊一乍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 不小心忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感觉发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}时间好像一眨眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我想至少在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用美好的回忆来结束这次旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次可能因为我们的家族内情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给你留下了不好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我并不觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能和大家一起像这样度过这个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我心里能感到的只有快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好期待明天的烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摩给太的特别动画快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱 一起去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 红叶哥哥说他也要看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想对于大家来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然也包括由希和阿夹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一定是一段宝贵的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.03,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摩给太讲的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.18,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}悬疑故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.80,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 也有很热血的情节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.92,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.09,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大杂烩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希来这里后发生了某些改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信一定都是非常好的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人没有叫你明天也过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我这么觉得 你会生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之前一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么你们会那么听话地把透扔下 去了慊人那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果没有选慊人 而是选了透的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那样只会让透的形象变得更差
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们 包括由希在内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是在保护透 不让她被慊人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这样说我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就好像我们做了一件大好事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我做得不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别的不说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如今还希望和透一起创造回忆的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最喜欢透的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也太任性…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起这个 你刚才是不是吵着要看什么电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我被夹勒索了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你把我当成哪里跑来的小流氓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶 动画片快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 摩给太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得赶紧过去看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是那个奇怪的动画片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我想更多地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿里 今天用藤球一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摩给太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.46,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要上了 摩给太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也想再多做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像大家给了我很多东西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我 我也能为大家多做些什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改变些什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到现在都还是一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次你怎么把红野也带了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是很中意他吗 中意到不想让他被别人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么 只是感觉他最近状态不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想让他稍微放松一下罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想他应该是压力太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}压力？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪来的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非要说的话 压力太大的人是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 还有什么让你不顺心的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然有 烦心事多了去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}举个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就让我很不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你对我一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全 一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直对你很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以前对我可要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼里只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更重视我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然你对那个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本家来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这帮人又擅自胡搞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把我这个大当家放眼里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人 只要你能出面 事情应该很快就能平息…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是楝她又在胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么 你很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是在往坏里想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红野 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个女人 那个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么来了 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是来见本田透的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出去散散步冷静一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}突然出了点儿事 我得赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我想起来我好像还没和本田透见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在吗 可是透她应该已经睡下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去把她叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人 你现在在生气对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生气的慊人是会乱发脾气对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么这么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么 告诉你又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想了解我 理解我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}理解？理解？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只是在蔑视我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只不过是站在道德制高点上 定义我的好坏罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是在命令我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这人还真是令人生厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是透 本田透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是特地来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管你对我的态度多么恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有些事情我还是得告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你以为自己拯救了由希还有夹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我劝你赶紧为你的不自量感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}高中毕业后就会被幽禁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和在他之前的那个猫附身一样 会被关一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有由希 以及所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这辈子都只能活在草摩家 活在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直到死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十二生肖里的所有人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在同一个地点 同一个场所 以同样的步调活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用争抢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不会被夺走什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幸福的未来 永无止境的宴席
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永恒不变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我是不会让你加入我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我是不会让你加入我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可那真的是幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幽禁 回到草摩家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永恒不变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么大家已经开始试图 试图前行的心愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能不能请你不要把这说得像是件坏事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这样的局外人和我们 说到底连活法都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的事还没有单纯到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以用你的那些脆弱的价值观来评判是非
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是十二生肖中的鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人和大家都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不同的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对十二生肖来说 你是怎样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神对动物们说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我对所有的十二生肖来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是如同神一般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是掌管他们灵魂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是他们灵魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人 终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉红野 我非常想来和她打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是草摩红野 十二生肖中的鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鸡属相 这位就是十二生肖中的鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所有的十二生肖最终都必定会回到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我们是无法被分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以请你别再来破坏我们的幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别瞎掺和 老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否则
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会受到惩罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人是神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是立于十二支顶端的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是大家都不敢反抗的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么诅咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未知的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一切的根源 同时束缚着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}束缚着大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也束缚着…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小波 伤口交给我来处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是要跟慊人一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}波鸟先生 紫吴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让他们稍等一会应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们怎么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶他一脸惊慌地跑来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还以为出什么大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶也受伤了 红叶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用担心 他就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何其美丽的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这次红叶真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相比之下那几个年轻人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该是相比之下「我们」 才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看 人已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶他一定会跑去叫大人过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自己窝囊成这样 令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来那家伙也曾觉得自己窝囊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讽刺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁让保护别人这种事 并不简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝对不准说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要保护别人并不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也想要保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保护给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放晴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雨停了 可以放烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在吗 天还没黑透
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经等不及天黑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那啥 为什么你们两个都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天夜里散步的时候摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对吧 红叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们是同命相连
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是同病相怜才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们 不是要放烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从哪种开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一棒我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呃 这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗 我只觉得呛人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹以前见过这种黑蛇烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 小时候见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有一次师父听我说还没放过烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就买了一大堆回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是我第一次知道还有这么好玩的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过放烟花这种事你也一定经历过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和妈妈一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有过 玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妈妈她似乎一看到火和打架就会热血沸腾起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不良少女的血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 你读下说明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}垂直朝上 插入瓶子之类的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}点燃引信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可以拿在手里 也不能对着人或建筑物燃放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你正对着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.80,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.90,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹一定能躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.04,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.53,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用你相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我们来放礼花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混蛋 不要对着人放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瞧 要爆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烟花本来就这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}师父将烟花的光亮带到夹的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不是为了那个被幽禁的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希不断反抗 也绝不是为了回到草摩家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想在大家内心深处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该都有一个可以畅想自由的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果诅咒会将这些都束缚住的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我希望能帮他们解除诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道自己没有自知之明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保护这个词 光是嘴上说说的话很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别瞎掺和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 即使是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}卸去所有束缚的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是能迎来可以发自内心地哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}发自内心地笑的一天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算我会受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也想要解除诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家看起来都玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为大家还从来没有像这样聚集在一起玩闹过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽说夏天每年都会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但同一个夏天却不会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像这样和本田一起生活的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对我来说非常宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可以加入你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一起来放仙女棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹 夹也一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烦死了 你们几个玩就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那这样 要不我把位置让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蠢猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瞎扯什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不让座我也照样会自己找位置坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倔驴可真让人费神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倔驴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想保护大家前行的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽我的全力
