Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.85,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:07.07,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:12.24,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在由心发出呐喊时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:13.70,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.74,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:25.04,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}对自己坦率些最好
