Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:47.02,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要再一个人去承受风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:54.28,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我来为你撑伞
